IMPORTANT FORMATTING RULES: 1. If the conversation involves comparing existing vs proposed values, populate comparisonTable 2. Each row in comparisonTable should represent one parameter being compared 3. Use "Yes", "No", or "Partial" for matchDecision field 4. If no comparison is involved, return empty comparisonTable array 5. Always provide summary, keyTopics, actionItems, and decisions
